WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:01.726
Hello, Miss Billy.

00:00:01.726 --> 00:00:02.651
This is Brandon.

00:00:02.651 --> 00:00:08.525
Of course you know, but I just had this visitation that I have to tell you about privately on this.

00:00:08.525 --> 00:00:11.920
I'm sitting here after it was over, and the Lord said, "Make a video.

00:00:11.920 --> 00:00:14.520
Don't call her on the phone, just tell her.

00:00:14.520 --> 00:00:18.293
" So, this is what I saw: I saw Lucy.

00:00:18.293 --> 00:00:22.160
I saw Brother Halverson.

00:00:22.160 --> 00:00:24.034
I saw Jeannie Wilkerson.

00:00:24.034 --> 00:00:25.439
And they were...

00:00:25.439 --> 00:00:27.059
I'll tell you what I saw.

00:00:27.059 --> 00:00:36.204
I was interceding and all of a sudden tonight, I was caught up in the spirit, and I got taken, and I was hearing people sing with me.

00:00:36.204 --> 00:00:41.380
And I was singing, "From glory to glory, He's changing me, changing me.

00:00:42.280 --> 00:00:49.919
" And all of a sudden, I heard other voices in my room singing this song with me as I was worshiping in the glory.

00:00:49.919 --> 00:00:52.791
And Diana could smell the fragrance of the Father and Jesus.

00:00:52.791 --> 00:00:54.036
"I'm here with you.

00:00:54.036 --> 00:00:59.908
" And all of a sudden, I could hear, "From glory to glory, He's changing us.

00:00:59.908 --> 00:01:04.270
" And it was beautiful singing, and I was like...

00:01:04.270 --> 00:01:06.594
I noticed that voice before.

00:01:06.594 --> 00:01:10.444
That's Lucy, Lynn's sister.

00:01:10.444 --> 00:01:14.499
I said, "Honey, I hear her voice.

00:01:14.499 --> 00:01:21.072
" And all of a sudden, I was taken up, and I went through like this pillar, this shaft of a tunnel.

00:01:21.072 --> 00:01:26.640
It was like a tunnel, and all of a sudden, I went through this tunnel, and there was purple, and there were clouds, and it was beautiful.

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:29.510
And I went up through it, and I could see into heaven.

00:01:29.510 --> 00:01:31.360
And I said, "Lord, what is this?

00:01:31.360 --> 00:01:34.224
" He said, "This is the great cloud of witnesses, Brandon.

00:01:34.224 --> 00:01:42.149
They're praying with you tonight.

00:01:42.159 --> 00:01:50.320
" And I could hear Sister Lucy interceding for America and...

00:01:51.600 --> 00:01:54.640
I'll try to do this without crying.

00:01:54.640 --> 00:01:57.647
I could hear her singing, praying for her sister, Lynn.

00:01:57.647 --> 00:02:02.093
And I could hear her interceding for Minnesota.

00:02:02.093 --> 00:02:07.269
And she was saying, "Minnesota, Minnesota," and she was praying in tongues, a heavenly tongue.

00:02:07.269 --> 00:02:08.297
It was glorious.

00:02:08.297 --> 00:02:14.780
And they were interceding in heaven for America, for a revival.

00:02:14.780 --> 00:02:18.777
And I could see Brother Halverson, and they were praying together.

00:02:18.777 --> 00:02:24.469
And I could see Jeannie Wilkerson and Rachel Tippet Teafatiller, and there were two other people.

00:02:24.469 --> 00:02:28.200
I don't know who they were, but they were sitting on a patchwork quilt.

00:02:28.620 --> 00:02:35.770
I can describe it to you: Lucy was sitting in a rocking chair that was like a beautiful, old, oak rocking chair.

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:39.440
It was all Southern-looking.

00:02:42.940 --> 00:02:45.480
It was beautiful.

00:02:45.480 --> 00:02:49.729
And they were sitting on a grassy meadow with a beautiful oak tree.

00:02:49.729 --> 00:02:53.609
And this oak tree was gorgeous, and there was no darkness in it at all.

00:02:53.609 --> 00:02:56.800
None of the leaves had shadows.

00:02:56.800 --> 00:03:00.142
All of this oak tree was beautiful, shining bright.

00:03:00.142 --> 00:03:04.000
And I could see it as I was looking through this portal.

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:11.706
And I could see Jeannie Wilkerson was sitting next to this lady that had a bun in her hair.

00:03:11.706 --> 00:03:19.360
She looked like she had a big, Holy Ghost Pentecostal haircut, like her hair was pulled up and it was in a bun on top of a bun.

00:03:20.974 --> 00:03:28.060
She looked like an old Pentecostal woman, and they were all travailing for Minnesota.

00:03:28.060 --> 00:03:31.770
And I could see Brother Halverson, but they looked young-looking.

00:03:35.431 --> 00:03:41.920
Of course, they were in their glorified bodies, but the Lord said, "Brandon, they're interceding for the revival.

00:03:41.920 --> 00:03:44.080
They're travailing for the revival.

00:03:44.080 --> 00:03:46.103
" But as I could see...

00:03:46.103 --> 00:03:46.274
Okay.

00:03:46.274 --> 00:03:47.379
Oh, the Lord said, "Don't skip around.

00:03:47.379 --> 00:03:49.519
" I got to tell you about the patchwork quilt.

00:03:49.519 --> 00:03:53.460
The patchwork quilt had pastel colors.

00:03:53.460 --> 00:04:02.057
I could see purple, blue, pink, and white on this quilt that Sister Wilkerson was sitting on with these other women.

00:04:05.060 --> 00:04:07.416
And like I said, Lucy was in the chair.

00:04:07.416 --> 00:04:10.080
And Brother Halverson was sitting next to Lucy.

00:04:10.080 --> 00:04:24.011
And I could see him, and I could see the quilt was on the ground, but there were flowers, these beautiful little daisies on top of the purple square-looking quilt pattern.

00:04:24.011 --> 00:04:27.424
And each daisy was perfectly in a row.

00:04:27.424 --> 00:04:33.900
And I could see yellow threads come up through where each square would be connected to each other.

00:04:36.389 --> 00:04:43.680
In those little squares were little yellow threads that were like bows.

00:04:43.680 --> 00:04:52.080
Beautiful little bows were inside of those little squares of this patchwork quilt, and they were having intercession.

00:04:52.080 --> 00:05:04.946
And all of a sudden, I could see Minnesota, and then Lynn Hammond's church became on fire, and a great wave of the glory of God...

00:05:04.946 --> 00:05:13.199
The Lord said to me, He said, "I visited it once before.

00:05:13.199 --> 00:05:18.993
But what I'm about to do at Living Word, son, will dwarf what I've done before.

00:05:18.993 --> 00:05:26.667
For a great, mighty harvest, a great move of My presence will visit in another generation.

00:05:26.667 --> 00:05:31.600
For I visited this generation, Lynn, and a new way for a new generation.

00:05:31.600 --> 00:05:34.880
A new way for a new generation is what the Father said.

00:05:34.880 --> 00:05:37.039
A new way for a new generation.

00:05:37.039 --> 00:05:42.120
And I will visit Living Word one more time with this great move of My presence.

00:05:42.120 --> 00:05:51.280
" And I saw a glorious fire all over Living Word Church there in Minnesota.

00:05:51.280 --> 00:05:56.000
And I heard Brother Halverson was praying, "Minnesota, Minnesota.

00:05:56.416 --> 00:05:58.320
" And he was travailing, "Minnesota.

00:05:58.320 --> 00:06:02.240
" And he was calling for revival, "Minnesota, Minnesota.

00:06:02.549 --> 00:06:13.840
" And he was travailing over this as I was hearing it echo as Lucy was rocking in this chair, and they were both praying back and forth with each other, and I heard it.

00:06:13.840 --> 00:06:34.503
But this was what was amazing: as it was being travailed in heaven, their prayers went through that portal and it hit me in the chest, and it caused the prayer to come through me, and I started groaning the prayer out in the spirit realm that was happening in heaven.

00:06:34.503 --> 00:06:40.742
It came through the portal and hit my stomach, and it started to travail through me.

00:06:40.742 --> 00:06:42.753
And the Lord said, "Pray it out.

00:06:42.753 --> 00:06:43.572
They're helping you.

00:06:43.572 --> 00:06:44.372
Pray it out.

00:06:44.372 --> 00:06:45.279
They're helping you.

00:06:45.279 --> 00:06:47.320
There's a great revival coming to Branson.

00:06:47.320 --> 00:06:49.573
There's a great revival coming to Collinsville.

00:06:49.573 --> 00:06:52.396
You must help them.

00:06:52.396 --> 00:06:53.435
Pray, pray, pray.

00:06:55.512 --> 00:07:10.860
" And yes, He said heaven.

00:07:12.319 --> 00:07:21.430
I'm trying to get all...

00:07:21.440 --> 00:07:23.600
I could feel the glory when I started talking about it again.

00:07:23.600 --> 00:07:35.350
I could see it, baby.

00:07:35.360 --> 00:07:36.800
Okay.

00:07:36.800 --> 00:07:41.006
Heaven and earth are going to collide.

00:07:41.006 --> 00:07:44.060
The Lord said heaven and earth are going to collide.

00:07:44.060 --> 00:07:56.160
And He said, "In one moment, in everything that I've ever desired, the greatest harvest of souls, Brandon, everything's going to change in a 24-hour period.

00:07:56.160 --> 00:07:56.896
Watch September.

00:07:56.896 --> 00:07:58.251
Watch these months ahead.

00:07:58.251 --> 00:08:11.759
For the birthing pains and the labor pains will increase upon the earth, but My glorious church, Brandon, will rise with a great fire, without spot, without wrinkle, what we've all been believing for.

00:08:11.759 --> 00:08:15.380
But it will be the greatest outpouring of the Spirit of the Lord.

00:08:15.380 --> 00:08:17.977
" And I saw Minnesota, and I've never seen Minnesota.

00:08:17.977 --> 00:08:20.347
But the Lord said, "Brandon, Minnesota, Minnesota, Minnesota.

00:08:21.303 --> 00:08:23.360
Watch what I do in Minnesota.

00:08:23.360 --> 00:08:25.280
" And I saw a revival coming to Minnesota.

00:08:25.280 --> 00:08:27.058
And I saw a revival coming to Branson.

00:08:27.058 --> 00:08:29.431
I saw a revival coming to Eagle Mountain Church.

00:08:29.431 --> 00:08:32.655
I saw a revival coming to Collinsville, Oklahoma.

00:08:32.655 --> 00:08:38.320
" And He said, "Brandon, there's going to be hot spots throughout the world, around America.

00:08:38.320 --> 00:08:40.540
" But He said, "Watch what I'm about to do.

00:08:40.540 --> 00:08:41.420
There'll be hot spots.

00:08:41.420 --> 00:08:49.680
" And I was taken to ORU, and I saw the Mabee Center, and it was completely engulfed with the glory of God, and it was a flame of fire.

00:08:49.680 --> 00:08:51.280
It looked like a teardrop.

00:08:51.280 --> 00:08:54.373
It was fire, and the fire of God.

00:08:54.373 --> 00:08:55.406
And He said, "Brandon.

00:09:01.970 --> 00:09:02.280
" And then He said, "I'm going to shake all the temples in India.

00:09:06.320 --> 00:09:09.086
I will shake the temples down, the false gods, and I'm going to break them down, and there's going to be major earthquakes.

00:09:09.943 --> 00:09:11.720
" And I saw a major revival, a flood.

00:09:11.720 --> 00:09:15.257
He said, "I'm shaking it, Brandon, and I'm going to visit India.

00:09:15.257 --> 00:09:17.080
I'm going to visit China.

00:09:17.920 --> 00:09:23.086
" And I saw a great revival coming in like we've never seen before in these areas.

00:09:26.057 --> 00:09:35.600
And so, it all came out of the prayer as Lucy and they were interceding for a revival for America, for heaven and earth are going to be invaded together.

00:09:35.600 --> 00:09:36.649
They're coming as one.

00:09:37.519 --> 00:09:43.617
And I said, "Oh, Jesus, what a time to be living in.

00:09:46.039 --> 00:09:47.839
What a time to be living in these last days, ladies and gentlemen.

00:09:47.839 --> 00:09:49.600
Oh, I'm not talking to my crowd.

00:09:49.600 --> 00:09:51.769
What a time to be living in.

00:09:51.769 --> 00:09:52.769
Jesus is coming.

00:09:52.769 --> 00:09:55.028
And so that's what I had for you.

00:10:01.160 --> 00:10:01.440
But it was so beautiful the way the cloud looked.

00:10:01.440 --> 00:10:02.773
I wanted to see it.

00:10:02.773 --> 00:10:05.211
You've got to tell Miss Lynn, too.

00:10:19.360 --> 00:10:19.640
That would probably bless her.

00:10:19.640 --> 00:10:20.880
Maybe you tell Lynn.

00:10:21.119 --> 00:10:24.662
I just wanted to tell you, Miss Billy, because you're my friend.

00:10:24.662 --> 00:10:34.126
But I thought this is something that's so precious that I couldn't keep it to myself.

00:10:52.030 --> 00:10:52.420
I had to tell people what they're praying for us over there, our loved ones that have went home before us.

00:10:54.160 --> 00:10:54.400
And I don't even know Lucy.

00:11:00.720 --> 00:11:01.280
I don't even know these people.

00:11:01.280 --> 00:11:11.590
But they're praying for us, and they're interceding for Minnesota, and they're interceding for us—the great cloud of witnesses.

00:11:11.590 --> 00:11:12.750
Jesus is coming.

00:11:12.750 --> 00:11:15.440
And it's something that I'll never forget the rest of my life what Jesus just showed me.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
And it's so beautiful.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Our Jeannie Wilkerson looks so nice.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
Her skin looked so young, and in every vision I saw, her skin was so young.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
And in all the things I've seen her, she looks so old, but she was so young and so fresh.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
I knew exactly who she was, and Rachel Tiller and this great cloud before us.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
God bless you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
I just wanted to tell you about it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Thank you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
